source.name: Events for Maryland Lawmakers Hosted by General Assembly Lobbyists
source.description: Spreadsheet of events held for Maryland lawmakers during the 2011 General Assembly paid for by lobbyists and special interest groups.  This spreadsheet was built by Capital News Service's David Rauf and compiled from reports maintained by the Maryland State Ethics Commission.
